      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, if my blood sugar is low, why would i take insulin? insulin lowers blood sugar even more right? im just really disoriented right now and i feel like im going to pass out. maybe i actually am high? i feel so weirdly lightheaded. i think i should just take a unit of insulin to be safe so it doesnt spike too much while im eating.",
